&lt;div class=&quot;components__JobPostDescription-sc-1qa03o2-13 bjOjov&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;About the opportunity&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Senior Backend Developer&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;who will take ownership of crucial backend engineering activities at Kadmos. As a regulated salary payment provider in the shipping industry, we are building secure, reliable, and scalable financial solutions that empower seafarers and shipping companies worldwide. You will play a central role in shaping the backbone of our platform and driving innovation in a highly regulated environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you can expect&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the backend.&lt;/strong&gt; You will be responsible for developing and maintaining core backend systems, building reusable libraries, implementing complex financial components, and integrating with external service providers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work with independence&lt;/strong&gt;. You’ll be trusted to take full ownership of your responsibilities, while collaborating closely with product, compliance, and engineering teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Impact at scale&lt;/strong&gt;. You will contribute directly to a platform serving the global shipping industry, with the opportunity to design systems that handle secure financial transactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborative environment&lt;/strong&gt;. We value diversity, transparency, and teamwork. You’ll join an open and supportive culture where everyone’s input matters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you bring along&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5+ years of professional experience&lt;/strong&gt; in backend engineering with &lt;strong&gt;Java&lt;/strong&gt; Spring Boot.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Master&#39;s degree in Computer Science, Mathematics, or Physics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise in &lt;strong&gt;Spring Boot&lt;/strong&gt; and strong knowledge of modern frameworks, SDKs, API standards, and libraries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid experience with &lt;strong&gt;unit, integration, and performance testing&lt;/strong&gt; (JUnit, Spock, Testcontainers).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of building secure, reliable, and scalable systems, ideally in a regulated or financial services context.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive, ambitious, and collaborative mindset with a track record of delivering high-quality solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency in English.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nice to have: familiarity with &lt;strong&gt;React&lt;/strong&gt; and experience in building financial products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Why us&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🌱 Opportunity to work in a company with direct social impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;💰 Attractive compensation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🇺🇦 Open &amp;amp; International environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🏛️ Fantastic location in the heart of Berlin &amp;amp; flexible WFH policy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🥘 Free lunch at the office&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;💻 Latest equipment, to ensure you have everything needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
